{"data":[{"id":564021008,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":307595822,"title":"高中生对哥德巴赫猜想的证明有哪些错误？","question_type":"normal","created":1546272354,"updated_time":1546301579,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"b53d96e0c4530624cc0fcca16d796547","url_token":"fu-bing-bing-57-61","name":"张三","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-8aa03f3cf3e81ccbb6ae2c428d6b0174_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-8aa03f3cf3e81ccbb6ae2c428d6b0174_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/b53d96e0c4530624cc0fcca16d796547","user_type":"people","headline":"轻狂少年","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":40,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/564021008","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-eef4f3d933a3ffecafa65e919b172be8_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546321934,"updated_time":1546322165,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":6,"comment_count":1,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e我晕，跑到另一个问题回答了，才发现大家都在这里。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我来给更多吃瓜群众讲讲吧。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e错误真的挺小学生的，然后这位老弟用唯一的高中知识——命题与逆否命题绕了一圈，把黑的说成白的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当然还用错了，不知道是不是故意的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e以下详细说明：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e关于所谓“歌德巴赫猜想变式1”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e（他先定义-1为质数）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e命题：若-1是质数，则∀n∈N+，2n∈A\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e正确逆否命题：若-1是质数，若∃2n∉A，则n∉N+\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e他所谓的逆否：若∃n∈N+，2n∉A，则-1不是质数\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e重点：他找到了2n=2，2∉A，所以说-1不是质数，所以原命题成立！\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e（下面且不说很容易就看出2=-1+3，明显是属于A）\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e喂！-1是质数不是你的定义吗？怎么把定义推翻了？？\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e而且！你找的难道不是你命题的反例？？你都说了n=1命题不成立，怎么又真命题了？\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e后面几页全是这个思路，同理易知显然错误。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-0c8fdc551910ffe838ddbfbd94c76c03_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1536\" data-rawheight=\"2048\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-cb38b5ea08f65aee0cfb6b04bb7d14ab_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1536\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-0c8fdc551910ffe838ddbfbd94c76c03_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1536'%20height='2048'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1536\" data-rawheight=\"2048\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-cb38b5ea08f65aee0cfb6b04bb7d14ab_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1536\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-0c8fdc551910ffe838ddbfbd94c76c03_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-0c8fdc551910ffe838ddbfbd94c76c03_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e告诫这位同学，在你现在的学习阶段，命题如果通过冥想证不出来，就别指望绕一绕逆否就能证出来。另外，如果你真不是故意的，建议考虑理转文。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e最后，举报你了 \u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hash=\"7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\"\u003e@证明\u003c/a\u003e 。不是因为你数学不够好，也不是因为你妄想证哥猜，有梦想不是坏事。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e问题是你证明出了一堆显而易见的错误，显然：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e1. 你数学本身不好；\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e2. 你没有给老师、同学检查过。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e那你就来网络上消费大众？只能说这件事你的本心就是值得批判的。举报不是恶意，只是希望你能借此认真审视一下自己，脚踏实地地前行。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"我晕，跑到另一个问题回答了，才发现大家都在这里。 我来给更多吃瓜群众讲讲吧。错误真的挺小学生的，然后这位老弟用唯一的高中知识——命题与逆否命题绕了一圈，把黑的说成白的。当然还用错了，不知道是不是故意的。 以下详细说明： 关于所谓“歌德巴赫猜…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=118\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=116\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","totals":489}}
